A character() vector of GENCODE or ENSEMBL transcripts.

A character() vector of GENCODE or ENSEMBL transcripts.

arg_name1

A character(1) vector of description of tx1

arg_name2

A character(1) vector of description of tx2

Value

A character() vector of transcripts in tx2 that are in tx1.
